org.moeaframework.util.tree
Class Min

java.lang.Object
  org.moeaframework.util.tree.Node
      org.moeaframework.util.tree.Min

public class Min
extends Node

The node for calculating the minimum value of the two arguments. The inputs and outputs to this node are shown below:

Name Type Description
Argument 1 Number The first number
Argument 2 Number The second number
Return Value Number The smaller of the two numbers

See Also:
Math.min(long, long), Math.min(double, double)
